From Maryland Directions/Parking Back to Top NAEYC follows the federal government’s policies on closing due to inclement weather.  If for any reason the federal government decides to close, NAEYC will too close, and all scheduled events will be canceled.  Any payments made will be refunded.  Meeting attendees will not be allowed in the building.  Information will be given out to any participant calling requesting additional information. If the event the government is delayed for two hours NAEYC officially opens at 10:00 am, and meetings will begin at that time.
